snippet.textDisplay: While watching this video, two sayings I like to live by came to mind - "Waste not, want not," and Time is money."  I struggle with these all the time, and, in this case, I feel the money saved, is not worth the time spent.  Unless you really want the "bragging rights," I'd rather just go out and buy a clamp that does exactly what his does. I still enjoyed the video, and, if you have time to kill and those spare pieces lying around, go for it.

snippet.textDisplay: I watched, spellbound, from the beginning and couldn't quite figure out what he was making. At first I thought perhaps it was going to be something to assist in the manufacture of a musical instrument. Or maybe a piece of hand-built navigational equipment for a boat. Or even, perhaps, something to launch rocket propelled projectiles into space. In the end it turned out to be a cheapo clamp which could have been obtained quicker at any D.I.Y. store, and without all the effort. Still, it did keep me from beating the kids for ten minutes during the current lock-down. Now, where did I put my cudgel?

snippet.textDisplay:
Cool idea.... You do have alot of knowledge... I would love to suggest you polish your skills in safety.... This is not a cut down to your knees....
I counted to make sure I still had all my fingers...
I have never been afraid to swing a hammer or use power tools to take on a project. I had to take the time to listen when someone was sincerely showing me how to make the tools work for me... This also meant to respect them (the tools also) to learn the handling of the tools safely.... So I could come back the following day to finish what I had started.
I truly do not want you to be discouraged with all of the comments from woodworking & crafting... I see alot of talent....
I just don't want you to be seriously injured. It happens fast... TOO FAST!
Please Practice Safety.
I hope you will watch your video & see what we're seeing.

I am a first timer viewer.... Normaly I can be on a channel a couple 2 or 3 weeks before I comment...
Just a concern channel fan.... K
:)
